# Public FAME deployment config.
#
# This file intentionally contains only public chain IDs and contract addresses.
# Load it before Doppler when running scripts locally:
#
#   set -a
#   source config/fame-public.env
#   set +a
#   doppler run -- forge test
#
# Secrets such as RPC URLs, private keys, mnemonics, explorer API keys, and
# upload/snipe keys belong in Doppler, not in this file.

# Ethereum Sepolia.
